		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 30 ft. Cone (Self) - 1 Minute</p><p><strong>[[/save CON 15]]{Constitution Save (DC 15)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 5d8 Thunder]] damage and is &amp;Reference[Deafened]. Glass or crystal objects in the Cone that aren't being worn or carried take [[/damage 10d8 Thunder]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success: </strong>Half damage, no effect.</p></li><li><p>This emits a thunderous blast that is audible out to 600 feet.</p></li><li><p>Each use of the horn's magic has a 20 percent chance of causing the horn to explode. The explosion deals [[/damage 10d6 Force]] damage to the user and destroys the horn.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Horn of Blasting</strong> activity will return 1 if it explodes otherwise it will return 0.</p></section>",
